readable.content: a woman in a black overcoat and red hair with man in white walking behind her A woman wearing a black coat and sunglasses is standing in front of a man walking away with a backpack . A woman wears sunglasses and a black coat as she walks . There is a woman in a black jacket and sunglasses and a man in a white shirt with his back turned . The woman in the dark coat is facing the camera , while the man in the blue shirt faces away .
